OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUK energy bills to be cut  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fby hundreds as part of     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FÂ£10bn support package     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, UK households are set to have hundreds 
OL,6, of pounds knocked off energy bills this
OL,7, winter as part of a #10bn package to   
OL,8, help people cope with soaring prices.  
OL,10,FThe government is to scrap a plan to   
OL,11,Fgive people #200 off bills from October
OL,12,Fwhich would be repaid over five years. 
OL,14,FInstead, the BBC understands that sum  
OL,15,Fwill be increased and possibly doubled,
OL,16,Fand will not need to be paid back.     
OL,18,FAdditional help for those on the lowest
OL,19,Fincomes is also expected.              
